02)--Filter: rank() PARTITION BY [window_topn_rank_eq_t.pk] ORDER BY [window_topn_rank_eq_t.val ASC NULLS LAST] RANGE BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW = UInt64(1)
03)----WindowAggr: windowExpr=[[rank() PARTITION BY [window_topn_rank_eq_t.pk] ORDER BY [window_topn_rank_eq_t.val ASC NULLS LAST] RANGE BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW]]
