02)--Filter: dense_rank() PARTITION BY [window_topn_dense_rank_t.pk] ORDER BY [window_topn_dense_rank_t.val ASC NULLS LAST] RANGE BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW <= UInt64(2)
03)----WindowAggr: windowExpr=[[dense_rank() PARTITION BY [window_topn_dense_rank_t.pk] ORDER BY [window_topn_dense_rank_t.val ASC NULLS LAST] RANGE BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW]]
